This archive contains the distribution Acme-Coinbase.

DEPRECATED - use Finance::GDAX::API or WebService::Coinbase

  Simple Coinbase API Test using docs at  
  https://www.coinbase.com/docs/api/authentication

    test with

      perl -Ilib bin/coinbase.pl

    Connects to a test coinbase account.

